msgid "11900:[name]セナ[line]「だから、はあ、はあ、一緒に……壊そう……」[%p]"
msgstr "11900:[name]セナ[line]So... hahh... let's destroy it together.[%p]"

msgid "12000:[name]セナ[line]「あの、すべての元凶を……」[%p]"
msgstr "12000:[name]セナ[line]The cause of all this...[%p]"

msgid "12100:セナの声が、ぼんやりする意識の中に響いてくる。[linebreak]やっと、立ち直ってくれたのか。[%p]"
msgstr "12100:Sena's voice echoed in my fading mind. Had she finally recovered?[%p]"

msgid "12200:そんなに、ぼろぼろに泣いて。[linebreak]僕みたいな、キモオタをかばって、血だらけになって。[linebreak]僕も、セナも、真っ赤に染まって。[%p]"
msgstr "12200:She was crying so much. She was covered in blood after getting hurt defending a creepy otaku like me. Both Sena and I were covered in blood.[%p]"

msgid "12300:でも、セナの熱さを、僕は、確かに感じたから。[linebreak]セナの声が、確かに届いたから。[%p]"
msgstr "12300:But I could feel Sena's warmth. I could hear Sena's voice.[%p]"

msgid "12400:一緒に、ディソードを振りかぶる。[linebreak]まだ、周囲で銃声は聞こえている。[%p]"
msgstr "12400:We held the Di-Sword high together. I could still hear the gunshots around us.[%p]"

msgid "12500:でも、もう無駄。[linebreak]さっきより、力が溢れてくる。[linebreak]セナからの強い命のほとばしりを感じる。[%p]"
msgstr "12500:But it was too late. The power was welling up inside me, stronger than before. I could feel the powerful pulsing of Sena's life.[%p]"

msgid "12600:神の力で、神に匹敵する装置を壊す。[linebreak]今度こそ――[%p]"
msgstr "12600:I'd destroy the device whose power rivaled God, using the power of God. This time, it would work.[%p]"

msgid "12700:[name]セナ[line]「行くぞ……西條……！」[%p]"
msgstr "12700:[name]セナ[line]Let's do it, Nishijo![%p]"

msgid "12800:僕はうなずき――[%p]"
msgstr "12800:I nodded.[%p]"

msgid "12900:セナと、２人で。[%p]"
msgstr "12900:And Sena and I...[%p]"

msgid "13000:[name]拓巳＆セナ[line]「うおおおおおおお――！」[%p]"
msgstr "13000:[name]拓巳＆セナ[line]Uwaooah![%p]"

msgid "13100:[name]セナ[line]「うおおおおおおお――！」"
msgstr "13100:[name]セナ[line]Uwaooah!"

msgid "13200:[name]拓巳[line]「うおおおおおおお――！」"
msgstr "13200:[name]拓巳[line]Uwaooah!"

msgid "13300:ディソードを、全力で振り下ろした――[%p]"
msgstr "13300:...brought down the sword with all our strength.[%p]"

msgid "13400:まさに、一閃だった。[%p]"
msgstr "13400:There was a powerful flash of light.[%p]"

msgid "13500:世界そのものを切り裂く閃光。[linebreak]赤い光が、夜空を両断する。[linebreak]月にまで届くかもしれない赤き刃。[%p]"
msgstr "13500:A flash of light that ripped apart the whole world. A red light that split the night in two, a red blade that seemed as if it might reach all the way to the moon itself.[%p]"

msgid "13600:それはあらゆるものを吹き飛ばし、消し去る。[linebreak]ノアⅡの見えざる障壁ごと、プラネタリウムを灰燼と化す。[%p]"
msgstr "13600:It annihilated everything it touched. The planetarium burned to ash, along with its unseen wall.[%p]"

msgid "13700:すさまじい衝撃と爆風。[linebreak]身体が千切れそう。[linebreak]僕らを取り囲んでいた連中も、吹き飛ばされていく。[%p]"
msgstr "13700:The impact and wind were incredible. I thought they'd rip me apart. The people around us were being blown away.[%p]"

msgid "13800:それでも――[%p]"
msgstr "13800:But still...[%p]"

msgid "13900:僕は、セナと互いの身体を支え合い――[linebreak]手元の赤ん坊を、２人でかばうように抱きしめ――[%p]"
msgstr "13900:Sena and I supported each other's bodies. We held the baby tight, protecting it.[%p]"

msgid "14000:最後の一滴まで、力を使い果たす。[linebreak]後のことなんて考えてなかった。[linebreak]チートコードがあれば、傷は治せる。[%p]"
msgstr "14000:And we used every bit of power we had. I wasn't thinking at all about what came next. With the cheat code, I could heal my wounds.[%p]"

msgid "14100:だから今は、ノアⅡを壊すことだけを。[%p]"
msgstr "14100:All I needed to focus on now was destroying Noah II.[%p]"

msgid "14200:ひたすらに。[%p]"
msgstr "14200:I kept pouring all my power into it.[%p]"

msgid "14300:己の気力を爆発させた――[%p]"
msgstr "14300:Letting it burst forth...[%p]"

msgid "14400:音が、消えた。[linebreak]光も、失われた。[%p]"
msgstr "14400:The sound disappeared. The light vanished.[%p]"

msgid "14500:廃墟と化した、死の街の真ん中で。[%p]"
msgstr "14500:Sena and I were standing there,[%p]"

msgid "14600:僕とセナは、たたずんでいる。[%p]"
msgstr "14600:silently, in the middle of the dead, ruined city.[%p]"

msgid "14700:セナは、僕にしがみつくようにして。[linebreak]僕は、セナに寄りかかるようにして。[linebreak]２人の間には、血に染まった赤ん坊を抱いて。[%p]"
msgstr "14700:Sena was clinging to me, and I was leaning up against her. We were holding the bloody baby between us.[%p]"

msgid "14800:一歩も歩けない。[linebreak]ほんの少しも、動けない。[linebreak]そんな力、残ってなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "14800:I couldn't move another step. I couldn't move an inch. I didn't have the strength left.[%p]"

msgid "14900:[name]セナ[line]「もう、いいんだ……」[%p]"
msgstr "14900:[name]セナ[line]Enough.[%p]"

msgid "15000:[name]セナ[line]「哀しいけど、もう、いいんだ……」[%p]"
msgstr "15000:[name]セナ[line]It's sad... but that's enough.[%p]"

msgid "15100:[name]セナ[line]「死んだ人を生き返らせるのなんて、エゴでしかないから……」[%p]"
msgstr "15100:[name]セナ[line]It's selfish to want to bring back the dead.[%p]"

msgid "15200:[name]セナ[line]「チートコードは、返そう……」[%p]"
msgstr "15200:[name]セナ[line]Let's give back the cheat code.[%p]"

msgid "15300:僕も、同じ意見だった。[linebreak]そして、僕たちは、生きているから。[linebreak]これから、死んだ人たちの分まで、生きて行かなくちゃならない。[%p]"
msgstr "15300:I agreed. And we were alive. We had to live our lives for the sake of those who had died.[%p]"

msgid "15400:[name]セナ[line]「ごめん……」[%p]"
msgstr "15400:[name]セナ[line]I'm sorry.[%p]"

msgid "15500:セナは、血に染まった赤ん坊を、そっと、抱きしめる。[%p]"
msgstr "15500:Sena softly held the bloody baby.[%p]"

msgid "15600:[name]セナ[line]「ごめん……」[%p]"
msgstr "15600:[name]セナ[line]I'm sorry.[%p]"

msgid "15700:[name]セナ[line]「死なせてしまって、ごめん……っ」[%p]"
msgstr "15700:[name]セナ[line]I'm sorry I let you die.[%p]"

msgid "15800:今日のセナは、よく泣く。[%p]"
msgstr "15800:Sena sure was crying a lot today.[%p]"

msgid "15900:でも、普段の誰彼構わずにらみつけてるセナよりも、[%p]"
msgstr "15900:But she was a lot prettier now than she was[%p]"

msgid "16000:今の、弱さが見えるセナの方が、キレイだ――[%p]"
msgstr "16000:when she was mad at everybody all the time.[%p]"

msgid "16100:そんなセナの流す涙は、とてもキレイだ――[%p]"
msgstr "16100:And her tears were beautiful, too.[%p]"

msgid "16200:そんなことを思いながら、僕は、夜空を見上げた――[%p]"
msgstr "16200:I thought about that as I looked up at the night sky.[%p]"

